name: SST - Society for Social Transformation
briefDescription: We imparted skill trainings in computers & fashion designing for sustainable livelihoods to 75 women & 50 youth.We conducted awareness camps and capacity building trainings on different issues to about 2000 women, 2500 children, 500 adolescents & 3000 Others.We provided relief to 500 flood affected and rehabilitated 50 street children & 200 child labourers.
